    "n1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "一个挑着空担的汉子看到关二狗，努了努嘴。",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    "n2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "巷口墙根撂了具死人子，路倒的，没得人认。拉切义庄，五文。整不整？",
      "next": "n_choice",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "n_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "jie",
          "text": "「五文就五文。死人钱好挣得很。」",
          "next": "c_jie"
        },
        {
          "id": "xian",
          "text": "「才五文索？……算了，拉就拉。」",
          "next": "c_jie"
        }
      ]
    },
    "c_jie": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_零工接活",
            "signal": "beishi_lg_accepted"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "c_jie_line"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    },
    "yan_offer": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "又是你嗦。正好——河头今早捞起个泡涨的，官面验过，没得人认。拉切义庄，八文。整不整？",
      "next": "yan_choice",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "yan_choice": {
      "type": "choice",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "jie",
          "text": "「八文就八文。淹的又咋个，一样背。」",
          "next": "yan_ok"
        },
        {
          "id": "buji",
          "text": "「泡涨的死人子沉得很……等老子缓口气。」",
          "next": "yan_no"
        }
      ]
    },
    "yan_ok": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "startNarrativeRun",
          "params": {
            "graphId": "flow_背尸_淹尸活"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_零工接活",
            "signal": "beishi_yan_accepted"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "yan_ok_line"
    },
    "yan_ok_line": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "死人子在码头巷口，苇席底下撂起。莫拖——日头毒了要出味。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "yan_no": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "要得，想通了再来。死人子又跑不脱。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "yan_remind": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "还没去嗦？码头巷口，苇席底下。手脚麻利点。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "yan_carrying": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "背都背起了还杵到这做啥子？义庄，快切！",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "yan_done": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "又来找活路嗦？要得——河头又捞起一个泡涨的，还是拉切义庄，八文。整不整？",
      "next": "yan_choice",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "c_jie_line": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "巷口墙根，苇席底下撂起。拉到义庄搁凳上，管事结钱。莫拖——日头毒了要出味。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "lg_remind": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "还没去嗦？巷口墙根，苇席底下。手脚麻利点。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "lg_carrying": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "背都背起了还杵到这做啥子？义庄，快切！",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "lg_placed": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "放下了就找管事结钱切，钱在他手头，莫来找我。",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    }
